import React from 'react'
import { Col, Container, Row } from 'react-bootstrap'

const Cv = () => {
  return (
   <>
       <Container>
         <Row>
            <Col md={6} className='bg'></Col>
            <Col md={6}></Col>
         </Row>
       </Container>
   </>
  )
}

export default Cv
